        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer7077004" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18198964499806398012">David S. Reynold&apos;s biography on abolitionist John Brown is well written and thoroughly researched. He paints a picture of a man morally and spiritually driven to end the institution of slavery. Interestingly, Reynolds also compares and contrasts John Brown&apos;s zealotry with modern-day terrorists who have also killed in the name of faith.</span>
  <span id="freeText18198964499806398012" style="display:none">David S. Reynold's biography on abolitionist John Brown is well written and thoroughly researched. He paints a picture of a man morally and spiritually driven to end the institution of slavery. Interestingly, Reynolds also compares and contrasts John Brown's zealotry with modern-day terrorists who have also killed in the name of faith.</span>
